WEBVTT

00:09:27.480 --> 00:09:30.560
of mosquito-born diseases,
of epidemics, right?

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:33.176
And better still,
imagine what would happen

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:37.400
if, in a very large area, everyone would
take these drugs, for just three weeks.

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:39.536
That would give us an opportunity

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:41.680
to actually eliminate
malaria as a disease.

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:46.296
So cheese, dogs and a pill
to kill mosquitoes.

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:49.280
That's the kind of out-of-the-box
science that I love doing ...

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:52.136
for the betterment of mankind,

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:53.776
but especially for her,

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:57.696
so that she can grow up
in a world without malaria.

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:58.936
Thank you.

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.341
(Applause)